,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e3e8445059dbca7f3aac3f278b393df078a340ae","tid":2061120,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:32:14.000Z","msg":"食懵你咩仲五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c9a20b2c81f7362e39c24aad6b40f952ee650c","tid":2061120,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"5大訴求不了 間接承認對政府有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33769483fc75c6da14c7ab90ae27eddca3dc1c90","tid":2061120,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"#15Jun #全港 #悼念梁凌杰 #全民黑衫<br />\n【梁凌杰先生逝世一年 - 6.15全城黑衣白絲帶日】<br />\n日期 : 6月15日 (一)<br />\n時間 &amp; 地點 : 任何地方<br />\n*民陣秘書署成員當晚將到太古廣場悼念<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMBG3ni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMBG3ni.jpg&h=7081e5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F3125&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=4021f237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCCOJoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCCOJoi.jpg&h=4d9b2333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#15Jun #全港 #悼念梁凌杰 #全民黑衫<br />\n【梁凌杰先生逝世一年 - 6.15全城黑衣白絲帶日】<br />\n日期 : 6月15日 (一)<br />\n時間 &amp; 地點 : 任何地方<br />\n*民陣秘書署成員當晚將到太古廣場悼念<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F3125&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=4021f237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125</a><br />\n<br />\n班黑警有機會介入或做大型SS，唔好以為悼念佢地就唔咬人<br />\n唔好忘記將軍澳尚十，過百人被SS，之後先放人走<br />\n<br />\nby 齊推行動做文宣巴打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">615 全港 黑衫、白絲帶<br />\n</span></span><br />\n民陣呼籲615全港黑衣、佩戴白絲帶，悼念梁凌杰逝世一周年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">615民陣回歸 黑衫白絲 PP悼念    620 大型公投</div></span><br />\n開到成個熱門都係615"},{"pid":"06dbd1edf9c371a7c5772c92322b48fda3419373","tid":2061120,"uid":187489,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"991d34dca15bbdc7f53bae354c3ed9f86cb171e3","tid":2061120,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:44:54.000Z","msg":"其實香港獨立喺200萬人心入面點諗<br />\n見好多人仲講緊五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇乜點提獨立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"有啲野冇得逼 要一步一步黎<br />\n上年有咁多中年人肯講光時已經好難得<br />\n<br />\n好似我自己 一路都好想有得獨但知道冇可能 所以都會唔一齊跟住嗌 不過好明顯每一次聲量都大過上一次 直到最近 我終於都叫埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都有中年人叫架 大家堅持"},{"pid":"82cc757dbd3221f2befd89a55f8268de5c4f4445","tid":2061120,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c769d9c9c736284e47a74760c029751a491ce6d0","tid":2061120,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ccbf3b61d4348fea71e811bdf97a8ac949b3d8b9","tid":2061120,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4e8a18303ba4493fb2ed2da26baaf5efbc08c8e6","tid":2061120,"uid":18999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae416cea949aa82a16b8622edad841498a40ed67","tid":2061120,"uid":330509,"like":0